Thousands have gathered for the Winnie Madikizela Mandela memorial service in Durban. 
Video : Zimasa Matiwane


Co-leader of National Interfaith of South African and Commission for Religious Affairs (NICSA) Vusi Dube led hundreds of mourners in song. 

In attendance are members of the ANC Women's which the struggle icon once led. 














