Thousands have gathered for the Winnie Madikizela Mandela memorial service in Durban. 
Video : Zimasa Matiwane


Mourners stood up, clapped hands and chanted Zuma while singing the infamous 'Wenzen u Zuma'(What has Zuma done).

The crowd also insisted that the former president, who turns 76 today be treated to a special birthday song, which a dash of 'We love you Zuma, we love you baba'.

The Mercury